# apps/backend/src/modules/flow/

## Responsibility
CRUD and analysis endpoints for automation flows plus decision-engine policy/evaluation APIs.

## Design
Router/service split with a validation-heavy service layer. The service normalizes flow graphs, enforces trigger/edge contracts, and centralizes app-id resolution and DB access.

## Flow
Handlers resolve app context, fetch or mutate flows, and delegate to FlowService or DecisionEngineService for persistence, execution history, test runs, and policy management.

## Integration
Uses Prisma automation-flow tables and shared app-resolution helpers; exposed under /api/flows and paired with decision-engine data for analytics/runtime behavior.

